reviewText: Sound quality not so great but a good buy

I have two of Muata Ashby's CDs for meditation and Adorations to Ra and HetHeru and also his Egyptian Yoga which I have had for a while so I decided to buy the DVD. I am very positive so it did affect me that the sound quality is in HD or close to it.  The most important is to learn the movements and free your mind.
I am really enjoying this. I wish the sound quality could have been a little better, but the explanations were most interesting.
